# Subagent Roles

- Parent orchestrator owns user communication, final decisions, and integration.
- `goodworkflows-state-manager` owns `workflow-state.yaml` only.
- DSL2 specialists handle workflows, modules, configs, channels, labels, and stubs.
- Template specialists handle rendered R/Python/Shell runtime behavior.
- Parity specialists handle launch templates, image manifests, workflow registries, and CI cache lists.
- Verify runners execute checks and report exact coverage.
- Docs/memory updaters keep user-facing docs and `memory-bank/` aligned.
